   "source": [
    "print(r\"||x_s - x*|| = \", jnp.linalg.norm(x_s - solve(A,b)))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Thermodynamic matrix inverse\n",
